                <p/>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Damanthès fils de Pithakos.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Damanthes son of Pithakos.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Damanthes figlio di Pithakos.</p>
            </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The Thorns suggested that the base was found in the Northern Necropolis because it is the only part of the necropoleis that was excavated by the Italian archaeologists.</p>
	<p/>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
